Miriam Forrester.

41
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:17,400
- Killed August '64.
- Car hit her on the street

42
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:19,500
by her house,
threw her into a ditch.

43
00:02:19,500 --> 00:02:21,300
It was two days
before anyone found her.

44
00:02:21,300 --> 00:02:22,900
I was a teenager
at the time.

45
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:26,700
Thought my sister was just
a repressed '60s housewife...

46
00:02:26,700 --> 00:02:28,400
- But ?
- Her husband, Harold,

47
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:30,000
