49
00:02:31,700 --> 00:02:34,900
Knickknacks, junk mail...
and this.

50
00:02:34,900 --> 00:02:37,500
- Tupperware box ?
- That was her big thing.

51
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:38,800
Drove old Harry crazy.

52
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:41,700
Real man-of-the-times, didn't
want the little wife working.

53
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:44,600
