57
00:02:54,500 --> 00:02:56,600
"I will hunt you down
where you live."

58
00:02:56,600 --> 00:02:57,900
Box was sent from...

59
00:02:59,300 --> 00:03:00,700
Hazelton, Mississippi.

60
00:03:00,700 --> 00:03:02,900
Two days before my sister's
body was found.

61
00:03:03,200 --> 00:03:05,700
August '64
was Freedom Summer.

62
00:03:05,700 --> 00:03:09,400
