126
00:06:12,500 --> 00:06:13,900
Sure.

127
00:06:14,100 --> 00:06:15,500
Bowling's good.

128
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:16,900
Saturday night ?

129
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:19,400
Maybe do a little
Italian place after ?

130
00:06:19,400 --> 00:06:22,300
It'll be good.
It'll be good.

131
00:06:22,700 --> 00:06:23,600
Everything okay ?

132
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,800
Yeah, yeah, I...

133
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:27,000
I just lost an earring.

134
00:06:27,500 --> 00:06:28,500
Oh.

135
00:06:29,100 --> 00:06:29,800
Where ?

136
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:30,900
You know where.

137
00:06:32,200 --> 00:06:34,600
Uh,  check for me, will ya ?

